---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="예쁨주의 쁨의원 - 프리미엄 메디컬 에스테틱" description="당신만의 아름다움을 찾아드리는 쁨의원입니다.">
	<section class="hero" style="position: relative; height: 70vh; min-height: 500px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; padding: 0;">
		<img src="/clinic_hero.png" alt="Clinic Interior" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; z-index: -1; filter: brightness(0.8);" />
		<div class="animate-fade-in" style="text-align: center; color: white; padding: 20px;">
			<p style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">재발을 최소화한 색소 치료</p>
			<h1 style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem); margin-bottom: 24px; color: white;">
				흑자/검버섯 제거<br />
				<span style="color: var(--accent-primary);">리팟레이저</span>
			</h1>
			<p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 40px; font-weight: 300;">상시진행 · 1회 시술로 빠른 효과</p>
			<div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; justify-content: center;">
				<a href="#" class="btn-premium">상담 신청하기</a>
				<a href="#" style="padding: 14px 32px; border: 1px solid white; color: white; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 4px;">상세보기</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section style="background: white; padding: 100px 20px;">
		<div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
			<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
				<h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">진료 과목</h2>
				<p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">쁨의원만의 차별화된 프리미엄 서비스를 경험하세요.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;">
				<div class="glass" style="padding: 40px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center;">
					<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">레이저 리프팅</h3>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 24px;">울쎄라, 써마지, 티타늄, 온다 등 최신 장비를 통한 탄력 개선</p>
					<a href="/laser-lifting" style="color: var(--accent-primary); font-weight: 600;">자세히 보기 &rarr;</a>
				</div>
				<div class="glass" style="padding: 40px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center;">
					<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">쁘띠 시술</h3>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 24px;">보톡스, 필러, 스킨부스터를 통한 자연스러운 볼륨과 주름 개선</p>
					<a href="/petit" style="color: var(--accent-primary); font-weight: 600;">자세히 보기 &rarr;</a>
				</div>
				<div class="glass" style="padding: 40px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center;">
					<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">피부 토닝</h3>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 24px;">기미, 잡티 고민을 해결하는 맞춤형 화이트닝 솔루션</p>
					<a href="#" style="color: var(--accent-primary); font-weight: 600;">자세히 보기 &rarr;</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="location" style="background: #fdfcf9; border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-border);">
		<div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr)); gap: 60px; align-items: center;">
			<div>
				<h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 30px;">찾아오는 길</h2>
				<div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
					<h4 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">주소</h4>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">서울특별시 강남구 강남대로 123 쁨타워 5-8층</p>
				</div>
				<div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
					<h4 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">지하철 이용 시</h4>
					<p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">2호선 강남역 10번 출구 도보 3분<br/>9호선 신논현역 6번 출구 도보 5분</p>
				</div>
				<a href="#" class="btn-premium" style="width: 100%;">네이버 지도에서 보기</a>
			</div>
			<div style="height: 400px; background: #eee; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
				<div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/initials/svg?seed=Map') center/cover;"></div>
				<div class="glass" style="padding: 15px 30px; position: relative;">지도 준비 중</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Floating Mobile Nav -->
	<div style="position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: white; border-top: 1px solid #eee; display: flex; justify-content: space-around; padding: 12px 0; z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 -5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
		<a href="/events" style="text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
			<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto 4px;"><path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/><line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"/></svg>
			이벤트
		</a>
		<a href="/reservation" style="text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--accent-primary); font-weight: 700;">
			<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto 4px;"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
			예약하기
		</a>
		<a href="#location" style="text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
			<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto 4px;"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
			오시는길
		</a>
	</div>
</Layout>
